<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>916</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men dōu kàn dào shén ài wǒ men de píng jù. wǒ men dōu xiǎng shòu dào, zhǔ de ài zài měi cháo měi xī.
 wǒ men dōu zhī dào shì jiè jiāng lái de jié jú. měi yī tiān de shēng huó yào duō jiǎn diǎn zì jǐ.
 fù a wǒ men de xīn dān dān ài nǐ. xiàng zhe shì jiè wǒ men zǎo yǐ guān bì.
 zài nǐ de guāng zhōng méng nǐ yǐn dǎo. shì shàng suī yǒu kǔ nán, wǒ men de xīn què wú bǐ tián mì.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men dōu kàn dào 迦南916</title>
</song>